query:
SELECT id, employeeId, employeeName, requestType, status, vacationType, vacationStartDate, vacationEndDate, vacationDays 
FROM employeeRequests 
WHERE requestType = 'vacation' AND status = 'approved' AND vacationType = 'بدون راتب'
ORDER BY vacationStartDate DESC
LIMIT 10;
